description:
At age ten, Bill Jensen and his "imaginary" friend, Yasu, inadvertently unlock a devastating power that kills three schoolmates. As adults, Bill and Yasu struggle to understand their extraordinary power, while encountering a cornucopia of supernatural creatures that secretly populate our world.

Dual is a comic volume from DC Comics' online imprint, Zuda Comics, that started appearing online June 2008.
name: Part One
